# Phase 6 Rules — Door Opener and Extensibility

## What This Phase Builds

- Door Opener Service: `DOOR_OPENER` assessment type with public-data-only scoring
  - 11 of 65 items scorable from public data (applicability matrix enforcement)
  - Public listing/marketing data collection workflow
  - Public-data diagnostic packages
  - Door opener report generation
  - Upgrade path from door opener to full engagement (preserves all prior data)
- Extension SDK: framework for adding new connectors, diagnostic packages, scoring rubrics, and entity domains
  - Connector registration and validation
  - Diagnostic package registration and validation
  - Rubric version registration with weight-sum validation
  - New fact grain registration with ClickHouse DDL generation

## Prerequisites

Phase 5 must be complete: client portal operational, trend marts functional, recommendation tracking working, at least one full assessment lifecycle (create → score → report → deliver to client) validated end-to-end.

